data.text:
Submit tips to help Deputy Sheriffs in your area.

Please fill out the form below to submit a tip to us. Please fill in as much information as possible, however only those fields marked with an asterisk * are required. The name, phone number, and email fields will only be used if we need to contact you for more information. You may also call us at 304-357-4693.

Tips are generally monitored during business hours.
